Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:44.85,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.37,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:50.76,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
