Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:05.79,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと声を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:13.00,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
