Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:12.55,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.91,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:19.07,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
